org.timepedia.chronoscope.client.canvas
Interface DisplayList

All Superinterfaces:
Layer
All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultDisplayListImpl
public interface DisplayList
extends Layer

A DisplayList is a Layer with deferred execution.

Drawing operations on DisplayList are buffered and replayed later.

Author:
Ray Cromwell <ray@timepedia.org>
